GO deg (differentially expressed genes) and fc (fold change) template data.

Source: R/go_deg_fc.R
go_deg_fc.Rd

GO deg (differentially expressed genes) and fc (fold change) template data.

Usage

data(go_deg_fc)

Format

Dataframe: include columns (id, log2FC).

References

https://github.com/BioSciTools/BioSciToolsDatasets/tree/main/GOenrichStat/

Author

benben-miao

Examples

# 1. Library TOmicsVis package
library(TOmicsVis)

# 2. Load example data
data(go_deg_fc)

# 3. View example data
go_deg_fc
